## 1. Project Overview

**S-KILLING IT** is a focused execution platform built to close the skill gap in college education. Students typically understand concepts but struggle to apply them consistently. The platform enforces a habit of daily, structured, proof-based execution.

### Core Concept

> *"Learning is incomplete without consistent execution."*

The platform converts passive learning into active building through:

- **Daily task-driven workflow** — Users receive practical, focused tasks each day
- **Time-bound execution** — A fixed cycle window reduces procrastination
- **Mandatory proof-based submission** — Code, images, videos, or links as evidence of work
- **Streak & consistency tracking** — Daily completion is measured and displayed
- **AI-powered mentorship** — Gemini AI generates tasks and answers questions

